TARGET:  color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.875rem; letter-spacing: 0.16px;
```

**Card dividers — `.screening-row` separators**
```
CURRENT: Uses ::before pseudo-element with border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
KEEP AS IS — this pattern works.
```

**Action bar — `.screening-actions-bar .button`**
```
CURRENT: font-size: 1.08rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
